<dashboard version="1.1" stylesheet="destine_footer.css" script="destine_footer.js" hideEdit="false" hideSplunkBar="false" hideExport="true">
  <label>Home</label>
  <row>
    <panel depends="$hidden$">
      <html>
          <style>
            height:100%;
            .edit-other { visibility: hidden !important; }
            h1.dashboard-header-title {
              color: transparent;
            }
            html {
              background-color: #ea2a8d;
            }
            .dashboard-header-description {
              font-size: 36px;
              font-weight: bold;
              color: white;
            }
            .dashboard-body { 
              background-image: url('../../static/app/dua-uad/home-bkg.jpg');
              background-size: cover;
              background-position-x: center;
              background-position-y: top;
              background-repeat: no-repeat;
              height: 91vh;
            }
            .dashboard-panel {
              border-radius:15px;
              border-width: 1px;
              border-color: #ea2a8d;
              border-style: solid;
            }
            .dashboard-row .dashboard-panel {
              background-color: transparent !important;
            	border-style: unset;
            }
            #row_1 { width:100% !important; }
              #header_0 .dashboard-panel { width:100% !important; }
            #row_2 { width:70% !important; }
              #pnl_about .dashboard-panel { width:100% !important; }
            #row_99 { width:100% !important; }
              #footer_1 { width:100% !important; }
          </style>
        </html>
    </panel>
  </row>
  <row id="row_1">
    <panel id="header_0">
      <html>
        <style>
          #header_0 .dashboard-panel {
            border-radius: 0px;
            border-width: 0px;
            border-color: transparent;
            background-color: transparent;
            margin-top: 0px !important;
            margin-bottom: 0px !important;
            margin-right: auto;
            margin-left: 0px !important;
          }
          #header_0 .panel-body.html {
            vertical-align: top;
          }
          #header_0 img {
            padding: 10px;
            vertical-align: middle;
          }
        </style>
        <img src="../../static/app/dua-uad/DE-EC-01.svg" alt="DestinE" width="450" height="auto" />
        <br></br>
        <img src="../../static/app/dua-uad/Exprivia.png" alt="Exprivia" width="150" height="auto"/>
      </html>
    </panel>
  </row>
  <row id="row_2">
    <panel id="pnl_about">
      <html>
        <style>
          #pnl_about .dashboard-panel {
            height:200px !important;
            border-radius:0px;
            border-width: 1px;
            border-color: #FFFFFF;
            background-color: transparent;
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            margin-top: 60px !important;
            margin-bottom: 0px !important;
            margin-right: 0px !important;
            margin-left: auto;
          }
          #pnl_about .panel-body.html {
            font-size: 16px !important;
          }
          #pnl_about .panel-body p {
            color: white;
          }
        </style>
		<p>The DestinE Usage Assessment (DUA) framework services is to provide a system capable of tracing and measuring the impact of knowledge, generated by DestinE associated assets and DESP registered services, in worldwide publicly available academic documents and policy.<br/>DestinE Usage Assessment Dashboard (UAD) Service consist on dashboards to visualise and manage information about DestinE, collecting summary statistics of Destine usage based on multiple criteria. It is developed and maintained by Exprivia SpA.</p>
      </html>
    </panel>
  </row>

  <row id="row_99">
    <panel id="footer_1">
      <html>
        <div id="destine_footer">
    	  </div>
      </html>
    </panel>
  </row>
  
</dashboard>